OL,3,CGovernment to impose 'restrictions on
OL,4,Csocial media' for under-16s
OL,6,FThe government has said it will
OL,7,Fintroduce "age or functionality
OL,8,Frestrictions" on social media for
OL,9,Funder-16s, education minister Olivia
OL,10,FBailey has said.
OL,12,FMs Bailey said the measures would be
OL,13,F"imposed" regardless of the outcome of
OL,14,Fa consultation that is currently
OL,15,Funderway into social media's harms for
OL,16,Fchildren.
OL,26,@oD@KOUpD@MO]uD@AOUuD@IO]
