OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777338232
OL,3,CGovernment to impose 'restrictions on
OL,4,Csocial media' for under-16s
OL,6,FThe concession by the government comes
OL,7,Fafter pressure from the House of Lords
OL,8,Fover the issue, led by Tory education
OL,9,Fminister and academy chain founder
OL,10,FLord Nash.
OL,12,FPeers voted four times to press the
OL,13,FCommons into accepting a ban.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
