OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777338232
OL,3,CGovernment to impose 'restrictions on
OL,4,Csocial media' for under-16s
OL,6,FMs Bailey told MPs: "On the remaining
OL,7,Fquestion on access to social media, we
OL,8,Fhave listened carefully to the
OL,9,Fconcerns raised across both Houses
OL,10,Fabout the importance of the Government
OL,11,Facting swiftly once the consultation
OL,12,Fhas concluded."
OL,14,F"The government has said repeatedly
OL,15,Fthat it is a question of how we act,
OL,16,Fnot if, but to put beyond any doubt,
OL,17,Fwe are playing a clear statutory
OL,18,Frequirement that the Secretary of
OL,19,FState must, rather than may, act
OL,20,Ffollowing the consultation.
OL,26,@nD@UOUtD@OO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777338232
OL,3,CGovernment to impose 'restrictions on
OL,4,Csocial media' for under-16s
OL,6,F"This brings forward regulations
OL,7,Fwithout pre-empting the consultation's
OL,8,Foutcomes, and does not ignore the tens
OL,9,Fof thousands of parents and children
OL,10,Fwho have already engaged with us.
OL,12,F"Let us be clear, the status quo
OL,13,Fcannot continue.
OL,15,F"We are consulting on the mechanism,
OL,16,Fand that is the right thing to do. But
OL,17,Fwe are clear that under any outcome,
OL,18,Fwe will impose some form of age or
OL,19,Ffunctionality restrictions for
OL,20,Fchildren under 16.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
