OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777338232
OL,3,CGovernment to impose 'restrictions on
OL,4,Csocial media' for under-16s
OL,6,F"I can also confirm that consideration
OL,7,Fof restrictions such as curfews will
OL,8,Fbe in addition, not instead of this."
